      "message": "Why are we using these unpackProperties rather than the generated bindings?  If there is something to add to sdbusplus, we should do that, but unpackProperties isn\u0027t something we should be doing in newer async code.",
      "revId": "9d7dfe1f91e8c8f56248ada11fcf4493dc49ee55",
